Author: conceptedge
Content: Pay $20 a month and get Paypal Payment Pro. It will let you integrate the payment collection directly into your site. Paypal will process the authorization in the background (your backend sends something to Paypal and process the response). This way, through out the entire process, the user stays on your site. Paypal acquired Verisign's PayLink and Pay Flow credit processing, and those are available as options too (albeit more expensive)
